1
00:01:32,250 --> 00:01:34,950
[How dare you!?]

2
00:01:35,030 --> 00:01:38,030
[Episode 26]

3
00:01:53,509 --> 00:01:54,440
You sent her off?

4
00:01:56,710 --> 00:01:58,039
What are you looking at?

5
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:01,240
Five stars aligning.

6
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:06,380
I looked up
the Nameless's prophecy before.

7
00:02:07,230 --> 00:02:08,360
Five stars aligning

8
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,750
refers to
this kind of celestial phenomenon.

9
00:02:10,750 --> 00:02:11,750
Ancient texts say

10
00:02:12,590 --> 00:02:15,390
this is an omen
of the monarch being assassinated.

11
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,800
That's pretty accurate.

12
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:20,960
It's not like that.

13
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:22,770
Look carefully.

14
00:02:23,430 --> 00:02:25,360
Hasn't its tail already started to curve?

15
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:26,910
It's not a straight line anymore.

16
00:02:26,910 --> 00:02:28,040
What does this mean?

17
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:30,310
It means all of this has passed.

18
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,690
Ever since you defeated Tu'er,

19
00:02:32,750 --> 00:02:34,870
you've already started
to change your fate.

20
00:02:34,870 --> 00:02:35,800
Since when

21
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:38,280
do you believe in celestial signs so much?

22
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,940
I believe in what benefits me.

23
00:02:42,430 --> 00:02:42,960
CEO Dan.

24
00:02:43,950 --> 00:02:45,680
Tomorrow,
at the Empress Dowager's funeral,

25
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:47,140
I still want to be with you.

26
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:50,079
We've already discussed this, Wanyin.

27
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:52,310
But I just want peace of mind.

28
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,480
You're taking risks,

29
00:02:54,870 --> 00:02:56,600
leaving me here waiting alone.

30
00:02:56,630 --> 00:02:57,890
Think about how I feel.

31
00:02:59,150 --> 00:03:00,480
You'll only feel at ease

32
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:02,290
if we face the danger together?

33
00:03:03,310 --> 00:03:04,280
What about your position as Empress?

34
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,740
You don't want it anymore?

35
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:08,310
If we can't take down Prince Duan,

36
00:03:08,310 --> 00:03:10,240
this Empress title is just for show.

37
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:13,040
I don't want to play cosplay
for the rest of my life.

38
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:14,910
You mean...

39
00:03:16,590 --> 00:03:17,990
you'd rather die with me?

40
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:23,050
♪ A letter, a line of words ♪

41
00:03:23,340 --> 00:03:24,590
♪ Picking up the pen again and again ♪

42
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:27,060
♪ A cup of tea, a glass of wine ♪

43
00:03:25,870 --> 00:03:27,400
When I transmigrated here,

44
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:28,760
♪ Drinking alone, hard to get drunk ♪

45
00:03:28,430 --> 00:03:29,560
I already died once.

46
00:03:28,850 --> 00:03:31,340
♪ Words unspoken ♪

47
00:03:31,190 --> 00:03:32,240
I thought

48
00:03:32,780 --> 00:03:35,260
♪ Shyness unhidden ♪

49
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:35,160
I'd go to heaven after I died.

50
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:37,590
I didn't expect to be thrown into
this hell-level script.

51
00:03:36,910 --> 00:03:39,090
♪ Walking down a street together ♪

52
00:03:39,370 --> 00:03:40,510
♪ Shoulder to shoulder ♪

53
00:03:40,430 --> 00:03:41,400
There were many times

54
00:03:40,870 --> 00:03:42,870
♪ Raising my head, lowering my eyes ♪

55
00:03:42,750 --> 00:03:43,430
that I

56
00:03:43,370 --> 00:03:44,750
♪ Blushing slightly ♪

57
00:03:43,750 --> 00:03:45,310
felt exhausted and wanted to quit.

58
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:47,290
♪ A face flushed red at first sight ♪

59
00:03:47,870 --> 00:03:49,360
But because I have you on my team,

60
00:03:48,810 --> 00:03:52,150
♪ A smile like a flower in my heart ♪

61
00:03:50,910 --> 00:03:52,079
I somehow

62
00:03:52,770 --> 00:03:56,200
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

63
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,120
made it this far.

64
00:03:56,910 --> 00:03:59,870
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

65
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,560
We've done so much together—

66
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:02,190
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

67
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:02,060
preventing a drought,

68
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:04,080
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

69
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:04,000
defeating the Empress Dowager,

70
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:04,910
and allying with Yan State.

71
00:04:04,380 --> 00:04:06,120
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

72
00:04:06,290 --> 00:04:08,530
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

73
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,420
Even if it ends here

74
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:08,920
and the game is over,

75
00:04:08,920 --> 00:04:12,040
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

76
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:12,880
I still want to praise myself
for a job well done.

77
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:15,220
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

78
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:13,920
Of course,

79
00:04:14,570 --> 00:04:16,709
we still have many unfinished things

80
00:04:15,340 --> 00:04:16,510
♪ Still unchanged ♪

81
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:19,779
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

82
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,850
and many things to do together.

83
00:04:20,459 --> 00:04:21,820
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

84
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:22,950
I'm also interested in the business empire
Xie Yong'er mentioned.

85
00:04:21,950 --> 00:04:26,530
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

86
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:25,800
You promised me

87
00:04:26,510 --> 00:04:28,110
that no matter what happens,

88
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:30,090
you'd never leave me alone.

89
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:33,100
Do you want to break that promise?

90
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:37,890
Alright.

91
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,780
Then let's go together.

92
00:04:40,780 --> 00:04:44,340
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

93
00:04:44,860 --> 00:04:47,860
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

94
00:04:48,310 --> 00:04:50,240
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

95
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:52,030
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

96
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:54,040
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

97
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:56,560
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

98
00:04:56,909 --> 00:05:00,110
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

99
00:05:00,870 --> 00:05:03,280
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

100
00:05:03,350 --> 00:05:04,470
♪ Still unchanged ♪

101
00:05:04,950 --> 00:05:07,840
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

102
00:05:08,410 --> 00:05:09,860
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

103
00:05:09,970 --> 00:05:17,320
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

104
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:38,220
Her Majesty the Empress Dowager,

105
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,870
a paragon of virtue.

106
00:05:41,190 --> 00:05:41,600
With

107
00:05:42,390 --> 00:05:43,750
her passing,

108
00:05:45,190 --> 00:05:46,650
the country and the people

109
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:49,050
have lost a loving and kind mother.

110
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:50,870
How mournful!

111
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,600
The whole nation grieves!

112
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,520
Her virtue endures forever,

113
00:05:57,720 --> 00:06:01,000
and she will be remembered
with honor for all ages!

114
00:06:02,930 --> 00:06:04,980
[Spirit Tablet of Empress Dowager
of Illustrious Virtue,]

115
00:06:04,980 --> 00:06:07,030
[Loyalty, Filial Piety, and Benevolence]

116
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:21,000
Stop!

117
00:06:32,130 --> 00:06:32,930
Your Majesty,

118
00:06:33,820 --> 00:06:35,400
for this final stretch,

119
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:38,380
you must walk beside the coffin
with the Empress

120
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,550
to show your filial piety,

121
00:06:41,150 --> 00:06:42,270
so that everyone

122
00:06:42,630 --> 00:06:44,690
will know the kindness of your heart.

123
00:06:46,190 --> 00:06:47,320
The mounting stool!

124
00:07:11,890 --> 00:07:12,620
Your Majesty.

125
00:07:12,620 --> 00:07:14,640
[Spirit Tablet of Empress Dowager
of Illustrious Virtue,]

126
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:16,660
[Loyalty, Filial Piety, and Benevolence]

127
00:08:04,220 --> 00:08:05,420
Protect the Emperor!

128
00:08:06,270 --> 00:08:06,930
Assassins!

129
00:08:07,390 --> 00:08:08,110
Yulin Guards!

130
00:08:08,110 --> 00:08:08,960
Protect His Majesty!

131
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:10,750
You, come with me to catch the assassins!

132
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:11,190
Yes!

133
00:08:37,549 --> 00:08:38,260
That way!

134
00:08:46,990 --> 00:08:47,650
Kneel!

135
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:49,550
Kneel!

136
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,030
Your Majesty,

137
00:08:53,030 --> 00:08:54,440
all assassins have been executed.

138
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,010
However,

139
00:08:55,390 --> 00:08:57,270
I'm not sure
how to deal with their leader.

140
00:08:57,270 --> 00:08:59,600
Please make your decision, Your Majesty.

141
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,360
How could it be him?

142
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,180
Isn't this Zhao Wucheng,
wanted by the Imperial Guards?

143
00:09:07,180 --> 00:09:08,510
Wasn't he already dead?

144
00:09:08,870 --> 00:09:09,640
So...

145
00:09:09,870 --> 00:09:11,630
that body from before was fake?

146
00:09:16,530 --> 00:09:17,550
How could this happen?

147
00:09:17,550 --> 00:09:18,080
Exactly.

148
00:09:24,910 --> 00:09:25,970
You're quite bold,

149
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:28,510
trying to assassinate me repeatedly.

150
00:09:28,510 --> 00:09:29,130
Tell me.

151
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,410
Who are you working for?

152
00:09:38,510 --> 00:09:39,020
No one.

153
00:09:40,870 --> 00:09:42,330
I'm doing this for myself.

154
00:09:44,150 --> 00:09:46,010
But there is no grudge between us.

155
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,200
Shameless tyrant.

156
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,770
You're blinded by lust.

157
00:09:50,910 --> 00:09:53,240
Anyone would be justified in killing you!

158
00:09:55,550 --> 00:09:56,740
Well said.

159
00:09:57,030 --> 00:09:57,910
Quite bold.

160
00:09:58,720 --> 00:10:01,390
No wonder you were the former
commander of the Imperial Guards.

161
00:10:01,390 --> 00:10:03,120
Since you've escaped capture,

162
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:06,050
why did you come back to die?

163
00:10:06,410 --> 00:10:07,840
You don't really think a single stone

164
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,040
could kill me, do you?

165
00:10:09,150 --> 00:10:09,710
Speak!

166
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:12,030
Who exactly is behind this?

167
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:22,520
You just want me to say that name,
don't you?

168
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:23,620
Fine.

169
00:10:23,870 --> 00:10:25,400
I'll give you what you want.

170
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:28,080
The one who ordered me
to assassinate the Emperor is...

171
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,780
Prince Duan, Xiahou Bo!

172
00:10:42,870 --> 00:10:43,670
Zhao Wucheng,

173
00:10:44,060 --> 00:10:45,390
you claim I ordered you.

174
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:48,200
Do you have any proof?

175
00:10:48,270 --> 00:10:50,490
Everyone at court knows I work for you.

176
00:10:51,030 --> 00:10:52,290
Do I really need proof?

177
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:54,080
If you work for me,

178
00:10:55,140 --> 00:10:57,150
why did you betray me so easily

179
00:10:57,840 --> 00:10:59,240
and confess it publicly?

180
00:11:05,570 --> 00:11:06,370
Your Majesty,

181
00:11:07,030 --> 00:11:09,840
I served on the frontier
and earned military merits.

182
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:12,500
Rumors then spread
that the army was loyal to me.

183
00:11:12,870 --> 00:11:14,960
After I returned to the capital to report
and handed over command,

184
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:17,220
the Imperial Guards became mine as well.

185
00:11:17,270 --> 00:11:18,310
This Zhao Wucheng

186
00:11:18,550 --> 00:11:20,600
attempted rebellion on Mount Bei twice.

187
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:22,320
Without any proof,

188
00:11:22,670 --> 00:11:24,670
he claimed he acted under my orders.

189
00:11:24,790 --> 00:11:26,240
So I have to ask,

190
00:11:27,550 --> 00:11:28,790
who ordered him

191
00:11:29,550 --> 00:11:30,850
to frame me?

192
00:11:35,390 --> 00:11:36,630
Th-This assassin...

193
00:11:36,650 --> 00:11:38,110
I know him, Your Highness!

194
00:11:38,150 --> 00:11:38,990
Isn't this...

195
00:11:39,630 --> 00:11:41,890
a servant from Minister Yu's residence?

196
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:49,030
This one too!

197
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,750
A few days ago,

198
00:11:50,750 --> 00:11:52,000
when I visited the Yu Residence,

199
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:53,660
he was the one who received me.

200
00:11:55,790 --> 00:11:57,000
Minister Yu,

201
00:11:58,670 --> 00:12:00,260
why are you framing me?

202
00:12:03,870 --> 00:12:04,670
Your Majesty!

203
00:12:05,270 --> 00:12:05,750
I...

204
00:12:06,670 --> 00:12:08,770
know nothing about this!

205
00:12:09,270 --> 00:12:10,000
Th-There...

206
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:10,980
must be...

207
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:13,360
some misunderstandings!

208
00:12:13,630 --> 00:12:14,750
Your Majesty!

209
00:12:15,150 --> 00:12:15,880
Minister Yu!

210
00:12:16,230 --> 00:12:18,130
You usually seem so honest,

211
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:20,240
yet you're connected to assassins

212
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,790
and trying to pin this on Prince Duan!

213
00:12:21,790 --> 00:12:23,030
What are your intentions?

214
00:12:23,030 --> 00:12:23,600
Lord Cao!

215
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:25,120
Don't talk nonsense!

216
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:25,780
Minister Yu

217
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,790
has never been involved
in factional disputes.

218
00:12:27,790 --> 00:12:29,600
How could he suddenly be connected
to assassins?

219
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:30,130
Exactly!

220
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:33,440
Besides, Minister Yu
just became the Imperial Father-in-law.

221
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:35,040
Giving up his family's glory

222
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:37,880
and conspiring with a traitor
to kill the Emperor?

223
00:12:37,910 --> 00:12:38,670
Has he lost his mind?

224
00:12:38,670 --> 00:12:40,720
You can know a person's face,
but not their heart.

225
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:42,150
To know the truth,

226
00:12:42,150 --> 00:12:43,910
we should ask Zhao Wucheng.

227
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:45,800
Zhao Wucheng,

228
00:12:46,790 --> 00:12:48,030
what's your explanation?

229
00:12:48,030 --> 00:12:48,870
I told you,

230
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:51,390
I did it for myself.

231
00:12:51,790 --> 00:12:53,050
You didn't believe me,

232
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:55,180
and forced me to accuse someone else.

233
00:12:56,390 --> 00:12:57,750
I accused Prince Duan,

234
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:00,840
yet you didn't believe that either.

235
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:02,480
You, as an emperor,

236
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,510
are truly hard to please.

237
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:06,700
No wonder the one I love

238
00:13:07,970 --> 00:13:10,840
is trying everything to kill you.

239
00:13:10,870 --> 00:13:11,740
Outrageous!

240
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:14,600
How dare you speak to His Majesty
like that?

241
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:15,470
Commander Fu.

242
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:16,480
Yes.

243
00:13:16,910 --> 00:13:17,720
Search him.

244
00:13:17,910 --> 00:13:18,270
Yes.

245
00:13:20,630 --> 00:13:21,180
Stop!

246
00:13:21,300 --> 00:13:21,960
Don't move!

247
00:13:30,450 --> 00:13:30,900
[Ever since we met
at the New Year flower market,]

248
00:13:30,900 --> 00:13:31,360
[I haven't been able to forget you]

249
00:13:31,390 --> 00:13:32,280
[I know your feelings for me.
Yet I'm entering]

250
00:13:32,300 --> 00:13:33,300
[the palace tomorrow,
and we'll hardly meet again]

251
00:13:35,910 --> 00:13:36,710
Your Majesty,

252
00:13:37,030 --> 00:13:38,560
These are some love letters

253
00:13:38,560 --> 00:13:39,610
between him...

254
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:40,620
and a woman.

255
00:13:43,510 --> 00:13:44,610
And this is a...

256
00:13:45,270 --> 00:13:47,230
uniquely embroidered sachet.

257
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:01,660
Are these

258
00:14:01,740 --> 00:14:03,340
truly written by Consort Yu?

259
00:14:03,630 --> 00:14:04,170
Yes.

260
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:07,510
Even this sachet

261
00:14:08,690 --> 00:14:10,890
was embroidered by her own hands for me.

262
00:14:11,300 --> 00:14:12,700
The fabric of this sachet

263
00:14:12,870 --> 00:14:14,760
is silk tribute from Qiang State.

264
00:14:15,630 --> 00:14:16,290
But this...

265
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:19,260
This was only given to the consorts
in the harem.

266
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:22,360
And this letter paper
also looks like it's from the palace.

267
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,370
Could it be...

268
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:25,070
that Zhao Wucheng

269
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:26,600
is involved

270
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:28,260
with a palace consort?

271
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,880
Shameless Zhao Wucheng!

272
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:31,610
We can easily verify

273
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:33,740
who this evidence belongs to.

274
00:14:34,240 --> 00:14:35,180
At this point,

275
00:14:36,510 --> 00:14:38,310
you'd better confess the truth.

276
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:43,510
Fine.

277
00:14:46,050 --> 00:14:46,850
I'll tell you.

278
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:50,860
This person is none other than

279
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:53,520
the most favored Yu...

280
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:02,270
Shameless villain.

281
00:15:03,620 --> 00:15:05,550
You don't deserve to taint my ears.

282
00:15:12,390 --> 00:15:14,630
Your Majesty,
why were you so eager to kill him?

283
00:15:14,630 --> 00:15:16,560
Are you not going to investigate

284
00:15:17,150 --> 00:15:19,000
whether this sachet
was embroidered by Consort Yu,

285
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:21,000
or whether they committed adultery

286
00:15:21,390 --> 00:15:22,670
and engaged in illicit acts?

287
00:15:22,670 --> 00:15:23,400
Impossible!

288
00:15:23,550 --> 00:15:25,670
How could Empress Yu
be the person you describe?

289
00:15:25,670 --> 00:15:26,840
How is it impossible?

290
00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:29,770
These assassins
are servants from the Yu Residence!

291
00:15:29,870 --> 00:15:32,330
Your Majesty,
are you really going to strike

292
00:15:32,390 --> 00:15:34,590
your own brother for the sake of a woman?

293
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:39,510
Xiahou Bo,

294
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:42,600
are you staging a rebellion?

295
00:15:43,150 --> 00:15:45,880
Your Majesty,
you can ignore our brotherly ties,

296
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:49,180
but I must ask one question
for the sake of the realm.

297
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:52,200
The Empress Dowager
was always in good health.

298
00:15:52,630 --> 00:15:54,290
Why did she suddenly pass away

299
00:15:54,750 --> 00:15:56,340
after going to Mount Bei?

300
00:15:57,790 --> 00:15:58,880
And Zhao Wucheng—

301
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:01,310
how did he escape unscathed

302
00:16:01,480 --> 00:16:03,340
while under a city-wide manhunt?

303
00:16:04,310 --> 00:16:06,770
Did he really have an affair
with Empress Yu?

304
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:09,390
Deposing the Crown Prince,
crowning the Empress,

305
00:16:09,390 --> 00:16:11,840
killing loyal ministers,
favoring relatives by marriage—

306
00:16:11,840 --> 00:16:12,640
Your Majesty,

307
00:16:13,750 --> 00:16:16,280
have you been deceived
by the demonic empress

308
00:16:17,030 --> 00:16:19,050
and lost your judgment?

309
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,000
Your Highness Prince Duan!

310
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:20,840
Shut up!

311
00:16:21,120 --> 00:16:22,480
Can't you see the situation?

312
00:16:22,480 --> 00:16:23,790
The verbal battle is over.

313
00:16:23,790 --> 00:16:24,710
Soldiers!

314
00:16:24,910 --> 00:16:25,640
Here!

315
00:16:26,240 --> 00:16:27,970
Eliminate the demonic empress

316
00:16:28,150 --> 00:16:29,600
to purge His Majesty's side!

317
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,610
Yulin Guards!

318
00:16:30,840 --> 00:16:31,390
Here!

319
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:32,800
Protect the Empress!

320
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:35,140
Uphold the truth!

321
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:36,080
Yes!

322
00:16:36,870 --> 00:16:38,000
Kill!

323
00:16:38,120 --> 00:16:41,200
Kill!

324
00:16:49,680 --> 00:16:50,960
That scoundrel Xiahou Bo

325
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:52,360
has actually colluded
with the Central Army.

326
00:16:52,360 --> 00:16:53,620
Why was there no alarm?

327
00:16:53,670 --> 00:16:54,670
It must have been when General Luo
of the Central Army

328
00:16:54,670 --> 00:16:55,720
returned to court to report

329
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:57,150
that he left some men behind.

330
00:16:57,150 --> 00:16:58,840
Since then, they've been hiding nearby,

331
00:16:58,840 --> 00:17:00,750
waiting for Prince Duan
to give the signal.

332
00:17:00,750 --> 00:17:01,320
Let's go!

333
00:17:19,200 --> 00:17:20,160
Li, you...

334
00:17:20,349 --> 00:17:20,880
Are you alright?

335
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:21,410
I'm fine.

336
00:17:21,720 --> 00:17:22,290
Good.

337
00:17:22,510 --> 00:17:23,369
Where's Er Lan?

338
00:17:24,050 --> 00:17:24,510
I...

339
00:17:28,319 --> 00:17:28,720
You...

340
00:17:29,310 --> 00:17:29,710
You...

341
00:17:30,370 --> 00:17:31,670
Li, where are you...

342
00:17:32,150 --> 00:17:33,500
Where are you going?

343
00:17:36,570 --> 00:17:37,230
Er Lan!

344
00:17:38,110 --> 00:17:38,720
Er Lan!

345
00:17:39,590 --> 00:17:40,440
Why are you going up there?

346
00:17:40,440 --> 00:17:41,570
We're outnumbered.

347
00:17:41,640 --> 00:17:43,550
We must push the giant stone
down the mountain.

348
00:17:43,550 --> 00:17:43,950
Er Lan!

349
00:17:44,550 --> 00:17:45,090
Er Lan!

350
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:51,880
Prince Duan's men already went up there.

351
00:17:51,880 --> 00:17:53,110
You'll only die if you go up.

352
00:17:53,110 --> 00:17:54,640
His Majesty and Her Majesty
cannot be left unprotected.

353
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:55,880
Don't worry about me. Go back.

354
00:17:55,880 --> 00:17:56,370
Er Lan!

355
00:17:56,610 --> 00:17:57,180
Er Lan!

356
00:17:58,550 --> 00:17:59,110
I'll go.

357
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:00,350
I'll go, alright?

358
00:18:00,350 --> 00:18:01,620
What are you talking about?

359
00:18:01,620 --> 00:18:04,280
Li, don't you always
want to be a pillar in court?

360
00:18:04,350 --> 00:18:05,700
You must live to that day.

361
00:18:05,700 --> 00:18:06,500
You're right.

362
00:18:06,880 --> 00:18:09,030
I joined the court
to make a name for myself.

363
00:18:09,030 --> 00:18:10,640
So don't try to steal that opportunity.

364
00:18:10,640 --> 00:18:12,130
At least I'm strong enough

365
00:18:12,510 --> 00:18:13,570
to move that stone.

366
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:14,920
Li!

367
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,180
I am a woman.

368
00:18:20,960 --> 00:18:23,040
My presence in court is already improper.

369
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:24,840
Leaving is only a matter of time.

370
00:18:25,420 --> 00:18:26,360
Go back, Li.

371
00:18:27,680 --> 00:18:28,810
Great Xia needs you.

372
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:36,230
Li?

373
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:37,370
How inappropriate.

374
00:18:37,370 --> 00:18:37,930
Hey!

375
00:18:38,270 --> 00:18:40,200
Why are you standing here in a daze?

376
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:42,040
Er Lan is up there.

377
00:18:42,040 --> 00:18:43,500
Let's go save her quickly!

378
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:01,980
Catch that demon!

379
00:19:02,230 --> 00:19:02,800
Wanyin!

380
00:19:05,750 --> 00:19:06,590
Your Highness,

381
00:19:06,590 --> 00:19:07,670
should we strike while the iron is hot

382
00:19:07,670 --> 00:19:08,520
and just...

383
00:19:08,550 --> 00:19:08,830
No.

384
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:10,940
We'll hold her hostage

385
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:13,000
to force the Emperor to withdraw

386
00:19:13,510 --> 00:19:15,600
and return to the palace to be confined.

387
00:19:15,600 --> 00:19:17,260
The Emperor cannot die today.

388
00:19:17,830 --> 00:19:19,030
Especially not here.

389
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:23,180
He must be bewitched
by the demonic empress Yu Wanyin,

390
00:19:23,830 --> 00:19:25,830
and then go mad and die in the palace.

391
00:19:27,550 --> 00:19:28,240
Who are you?

392
00:19:28,830 --> 00:19:29,590
Go check

393
00:19:29,720 --> 00:19:31,320
where Prince Duan's men are.

394
00:19:34,400 --> 00:19:34,950
Indeed.

395
00:19:35,190 --> 00:19:36,590
Down there are all Prince Duan's men.

396
00:19:36,590 --> 00:19:38,550
Push the giant stone down the mountain!

397
00:19:38,550 --> 00:19:39,080
Alright!

398
00:19:42,590 --> 00:19:43,240
One!

399
00:19:43,510 --> 00:19:44,100
Two!

400
00:19:44,440 --> 00:19:45,070
Three!

401
00:19:47,750 --> 00:19:48,240
An Xian.

402
00:19:49,830 --> 00:19:51,290
If anything happens to me,

403
00:19:51,420 --> 00:19:52,610
protect yourself

404
00:19:53,880 --> 00:19:55,280
and keep the palace secure.

405
00:19:55,280 --> 00:19:56,080
Your Majesty,

406
00:19:56,170 --> 00:19:57,330
what are you saying?

407
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:59,700
I exercised with Her Majesty as well.

408
00:20:16,080 --> 00:20:16,840
You demon.

409
00:20:17,400 --> 00:20:18,980
I gave you a chance,

410
00:20:20,420 --> 00:20:21,790
but you didn't take it.

411
00:20:32,110 --> 00:20:32,830
Who are you?

412
00:20:33,750 --> 00:20:35,080
Mind your own business.

413
00:21:00,110 --> 00:21:01,310
Push harder!

414
00:21:34,840 --> 00:21:36,210
Dan, come with me!

415
00:21:36,550 --> 00:21:37,510
Mr. Bei, I can't leave yet.

416
00:21:37,510 --> 00:21:38,880
-I haven't make Great Xia...
-No!

417
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:39,680
We must go now!

418
00:21:39,950 --> 00:21:40,350
Hurry!

419
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:42,000
We're giving up the throne!

420
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:43,330
Your Majesty, let's go!

421
00:21:47,210 --> 00:21:47,880
Your Highness!

422
00:21:47,880 --> 00:21:49,160
-Your Highness!
-Your Highness!

423
00:21:49,160 --> 00:21:50,230
Hurry!

424
00:21:50,310 --> 00:21:51,750
Lift it up!

425
00:21:56,350 --> 00:21:57,080
Lift it up!

426
00:21:59,950 --> 00:22:00,830
Lift it up!

427
00:22:01,830 --> 00:22:02,500
My leg...

428
00:22:03,550 --> 00:22:04,850
My leg!

429
00:22:05,270 --> 00:22:06,130
Your Highness!

430
00:22:06,480 --> 00:22:07,040
Your Highness!

431
00:22:07,040 --> 00:22:08,240
Your Highness, how do you feel?

432
00:22:08,240 --> 00:22:09,160
Go back to the city,

433
00:22:09,160 --> 00:22:10,310
and get the imperial physician!

434
00:22:10,310 --> 00:22:11,820
Where is Xiahou Dan?

435
00:22:12,030 --> 00:22:12,510
Your Highness!

436
00:22:12,510 --> 00:22:12,830
Your Highness!

437
00:22:12,830 --> 00:22:14,030
That expert carried him away and escaped.

438
00:22:14,030 --> 00:22:14,690
After them!

439
00:22:15,030 --> 00:22:15,500
Yes!

440
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:16,310
Yes, Your Highness!

441
00:22:16,310 --> 00:22:17,440
I want him alive!

442
00:22:17,440 --> 00:22:17,960
Yes!

443
00:22:21,440 --> 00:22:22,280
From the looks of it,

444
00:22:22,280 --> 00:22:23,640
the outcome is already decided.

445
00:22:23,640 --> 00:22:24,720
Where is His Majesty?

446
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:25,720
Why isn't he here?

447
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:27,280
Hurry!

448
00:22:27,400 --> 00:22:28,750
-Hurry!
-Let's go!

449
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:32,040
Hurry!

450
00:22:32,800 --> 00:22:34,590
Prince Duan planned such a grand scheme

451
00:22:34,590 --> 00:22:36,030
just to usurp the throne.

452
00:22:36,480 --> 00:22:39,000
Now that Prince Duan is returning
to the capital unharmed,

453
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:41,310
could it be that something happened
to His Majesty?

454
00:22:41,310 --> 00:22:42,180
If His Majesty had died,

455
00:22:42,180 --> 00:22:44,270
Prince Duan
wouldn't have left in such haste.

456
00:22:44,270 --> 00:22:45,310
And if Prince Duan had won,

457
00:22:45,310 --> 00:22:46,710
it wouldn't have ended so abruptly,

458
00:22:46,710 --> 00:22:48,110
leaving this mess behind.

459
00:22:48,110 --> 00:22:48,550
Look.

460
00:22:49,880 --> 00:22:53,010
Even the Empress Dowager's coffin
was left unattended.

461
00:23:04,550 --> 00:23:05,350
You're awake?

462
00:23:06,350 --> 00:23:06,790
Get up.

463
00:23:16,680 --> 00:23:17,720
Why am I here?

464
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:19,260
You tell me.

465
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:22,920
Xiahou Dan!

466
00:23:23,990 --> 00:23:25,050
Stop the carriage.

467
00:23:28,790 --> 00:23:30,040
Stop right now.

468
00:23:30,480 --> 00:23:31,510
I was ordered

469
00:23:31,590 --> 00:23:33,350
to escort you out of the capital
at the risk of my life.

470
00:23:33,350 --> 00:23:34,680
No matter what happens,

471
00:23:34,680 --> 00:23:36,080
I cannot leave your side.

472
00:23:36,240 --> 00:23:38,400
I'm telling you
to stop the carriage immediately!

473
00:23:38,400 --> 00:23:39,800
Don't waste your energy.

474
00:23:40,400 --> 00:23:41,800
They won't listen to you.

475
00:23:43,030 --> 00:23:43,830
I must say,

476
00:23:44,310 --> 00:23:45,930
Xiao Tiancai is quite something.

477
00:23:45,930 --> 00:23:48,720
That sleeping drug
kept you unconscious for 2 full hours.

478
00:23:48,720 --> 00:23:49,750
You knew about this?

479
00:23:49,750 --> 00:23:50,890
I didn't.

480
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:52,200
I absolutely didn't.

481
00:23:52,510 --> 00:23:54,370
I was going to leave this morning,

482
00:23:54,480 --> 00:23:56,680
but Xiahou Dan secretly put you in here.

483
00:23:56,830 --> 00:23:58,310
He kept it from you

484
00:23:58,390 --> 00:23:59,650
until the last moment,

485
00:23:59,720 --> 00:24:02,650
probably to prevent anyone
from leaking the secret.

486
00:24:03,480 --> 00:24:04,400
Alright.

487
00:24:04,550 --> 00:24:06,170
Stop being so angry.

488
00:24:06,190 --> 00:24:07,730
He did it for your own good.

489
00:24:09,560 --> 00:24:11,400
How's everything going at Mount Bei?

490
00:24:11,400 --> 00:24:12,130
I don't know.

491
00:24:13,070 --> 00:24:14,020
I plan to

492
00:24:14,240 --> 00:24:15,920
find a place to settle down first,

493
00:24:15,920 --> 00:24:17,030
then send someone to gather information.

494
00:24:17,030 --> 00:24:17,760
Is that okay?

495
00:24:20,480 --> 00:24:22,680
Just enjoy the view outside the window.

496
00:24:25,960 --> 00:24:27,190
I'm finally free.

497
00:24:30,800 --> 00:24:32,060
Protect Her Highness!

498
00:24:32,130 --> 00:24:33,060
It's a tripwire!

499
00:24:41,550 --> 00:24:42,480
Are you alright?

500
00:24:42,720 --> 00:24:43,270
I'm fine.

501
00:24:43,510 --> 00:24:44,750
-Are you hurt anywhere?
-What about you?

502
00:24:44,750 --> 00:24:45,280
I'm fine.

503
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:46,640
Your Majesty,

504
00:24:48,070 --> 00:24:50,810
would you kindly crawl out yourself?

505
00:24:52,400 --> 00:24:53,290
Prince Duan

506
00:24:53,960 --> 00:24:54,720
ordered me

507
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:57,240
to escort Empress Yu
to return to the palace.

508
00:24:57,240 --> 00:24:57,920
It's Mu Yun.

509
00:24:58,720 --> 00:25:00,180
It's best if you're alive,

510
00:25:00,200 --> 00:25:01,800
but it's fine if you're dead.

511
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:04,960
Empress Yu,

512
00:25:05,800 --> 00:25:06,750
you'd better

513
00:25:06,750 --> 00:25:08,950
-climb out obediently.
-There's a gun.

514
00:25:09,740 --> 00:25:12,550
Don't make me set the carriage on fire.

515
00:25:14,790 --> 00:25:17,840
If your face gets burned
beyond recognition,

516
00:25:18,300 --> 00:25:19,350
-It'll be hard for me...
-Don't panic.

517
00:25:19,350 --> 00:25:20,350
Pull it out first.

518
00:25:20,660 --> 00:25:22,120
To explain to Prince Duan.

519
00:25:23,070 --> 00:25:23,440
Yong'er!

520
00:25:23,440 --> 00:25:24,300
I'll stall him!

521
00:25:29,880 --> 00:25:30,590
Mr. Mu,

522
00:25:31,440 --> 00:25:33,040
you've got the wrong person.

523
00:25:33,240 --> 00:25:33,920
It's me.

524
00:25:35,310 --> 00:25:35,880
Mr. Mu,

525
00:25:36,130 --> 00:25:36,950
why did you...

526
00:25:37,790 --> 00:25:39,390
You've got the wrong person.

527
00:25:39,480 --> 00:25:41,400
Isn't this Consort Xie?

528
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:43,720
Mr. Mu,

529
00:25:44,400 --> 00:25:46,170
you said Prince Duan sent you here.

530
00:25:46,170 --> 00:25:47,230
I don't believe it.

531
00:25:48,110 --> 00:25:49,960
You were dismissed from your position
long ago.

532
00:25:49,960 --> 00:25:51,270
You didn't even have the right

533
00:25:51,270 --> 00:25:53,110
to attend the Empress Dowager's funeral.

534
00:25:53,110 --> 00:25:53,890
I guess

535
00:25:54,480 --> 00:25:57,270
you're just looking for a chance
to redeem yourself

536
00:25:57,270 --> 00:25:58,870
and get back in favor, right?

537
00:25:59,350 --> 00:26:01,400
But after serving Prince Duan for so long,

538
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:03,860
you must know
what kind of person he truly is.

539
00:26:04,640 --> 00:26:06,160
He appears benevolent,

540
00:26:06,680 --> 00:26:08,250
but is actually narrow-minded.

541
00:26:08,250 --> 00:26:09,060
Look at me.

542
00:26:09,790 --> 00:26:11,400
I'm a living example.

543
00:26:12,400 --> 00:26:12,830
Mr. Mu,

544
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:14,680
take my advice.

545
00:26:16,030 --> 00:26:17,630
Prince Duan is no good ruler.

546
00:26:18,240 --> 00:26:19,720
His Majesty is kind-hearted.

547
00:26:19,720 --> 00:26:21,640
If you join me
in turning against Prince Duan,

548
00:26:21,640 --> 00:26:23,370
he will surely spare your life.

549
00:26:24,750 --> 00:26:25,480
His Majesty?

550
00:26:30,790 --> 00:26:31,200
He...

551
00:26:31,350 --> 00:26:34,000
He can barely save himself now.

552
00:26:34,870 --> 00:26:35,710
At this point,

553
00:26:36,160 --> 00:26:39,450
he might already be a corpse.

554
00:26:41,880 --> 00:26:43,180
You guessed right.

555
00:26:43,720 --> 00:26:45,150
My waiting here

556
00:26:45,170 --> 00:26:47,030
is indeed my last desperate move.

557
00:26:47,160 --> 00:26:48,600
I was taking a gamble

558
00:26:49,590 --> 00:26:52,050
that His Majesty
would send Empress Yu away.

559
00:26:52,680 --> 00:26:53,830
I was also betting

560
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:56,760
that they'd choose a secluded path.

561
00:26:57,550 --> 00:26:59,880
I pride myself on reading people.

562
00:27:00,440 --> 00:27:03,310
I should have been the one
skillfully balancing all sides,

563
00:27:03,310 --> 00:27:05,000
all the factions

564
00:27:05,160 --> 00:27:07,220
desperately trying to win me over.

565
00:27:08,110 --> 00:27:09,000
But now,

566
00:27:09,270 --> 00:27:11,330
I have to be

567
00:27:11,440 --> 00:27:13,650
a strategist without a position.

568
00:27:14,590 --> 00:27:15,400
Tell me,

569
